#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.68"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.68:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.68:0.2"
msgid "7. Migajālavagga"
msgstr "7. With Migajāla"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn35.68:0.3"
msgid "68. Samiddhilokapañhāsutta"
msgstr "68. Samiddhi’s Question About the World"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.40"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.68:1.1"
msgid "“‘Loko, loko’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘the world’."

msgctxt "sn35.68:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, loko vā assa lokapaññatti vā”ti?"
msgstr "How do we define the world or what is known as the world?”"

msgctxt "sn35.68:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Yattha kho, samiddhi, atthi cakkhu, atthi rūpā, atthi cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, atthi "
"cakkhuviññāṇaviññātabbā dhammā, atthi tattha loko vā lokapaññatti vāti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“Samiddhi, where there is the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and phenomena "
"to be known by eye consciousness, there is the world or what is known as the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn35.68:1.4"
msgid "atthi jivhā … pe …"
msgstr "Where there is the ear … nose … tongue … body …"

msgctxt "sn35.68:1.5"
msgid ""
"atthi mano, atthi dhammā, atthi manoviññāṇaṃ, atthi manoviññāṇaviññātabbā "
"dhammā, atthi tattha loko vā lokapaññatti vā."
msgstr ""
"Where there is the mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, and phenomena to be "
"known by mind consciousness, there is the world or what is known as the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.68:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yattha ca kho, samiddhi, natthi cakkhu, natthi rūpā, natthi cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, "
"natthi cakkhuviññāṇaviññātabbā dhammā, natthi tattha loko vā lokapaññatti vā "
"… pe …"
msgstr ""
"Where there is no eye, no sights, no eye consciousness, and no phenomena to "
"be known by eye consciousness, there is no world or what is known as the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn35.68:2.2"
msgid "natthi jivhā … pe …"
msgstr "Where there is no ear … nose … tongue … body …"

msgctxt "sn35.68:2.3"
msgid ""
"natthi mano, natthi dhammā, natthi manoviññāṇaṃ, natthi "
"manoviññāṇaviññātabbā dhammā, natthi tattha loko vā lokapaññatti vā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Where there is no mind, no thoughts, no mind consciousness, and no phenomena "
"to be known by mind consciousness, there is no world or what is known as the "
"world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.68:2.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
